{"word":"G1011 - βουλεύω - bouleúō - bool-yoo'-o - Consult","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βουλεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">bouleúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">bool-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Consult</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆலோசனைபண்ணு, யோசனை பண்ணு, யோசி"},{"paragraph":"to deliberate, take counsel, resolve, give counsel"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1012 - βουλή - boulḗ - boo-lay'/1012\">G1012</a>; to <i>advise</i>, that is, (reflexively) <i>deliberate</i>, or (by implication) <i>resolve:</i> - consult, take counsel, determine, be minded, purpose.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}